prod.desciption:
N/AArriving in its original form, the Air Jordan 1 Low OG Neutral Grey features a white leather upper with Neutral Grey Durabuck Swooshes. A white and Neutral Grey sole completes the design.

The Air Jordan 1 Low OG Neutral Grey released in June of 2021 and retailed for $130.
